                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/53584866/">唐安安</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-11-11</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">一年前读过《宫崎市定中国史》，现在读这个，真是叹服。举重若轻，娓娓道来，哪怕实际经历过也难以写出背后的渊源变化。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
